  "instructions": [
    "Whisk together teff flour and water in a bowl to make the fir-fir batter.",
    "Heat butter in a saucepan over medium heat until melted.",
    "Add sherry and bring to a simmer, then reduce to low heat.",
    "Add berbere spice and stir to combine.",
    "Add onion, garlic, and ginger to the saucepan and stir-fry until softened.",
    "Add fir-fir sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Pour the fir-fir batter into the saucepan and cook for 5 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Flip the fir-fir and cook for an additional 5 minutes, until golden brown.",
    "Garnish with parsley and serve hot."
